ws_endpoints.Rd

Web of Science Endpoints

ws_endnote_endpoints()

ws_incites_endpoints(out_type = c("json", "xml"))

.ws_incites_endpoints()

ws_tipms_endpoints()

ws_wos_endpoints()

ws_woslite_endpoints()

ws_endpoints(out_type = c("json", "xml"), api = NULL)

Arguments

out_type

output type, either json or json
api

The API being used

Value

A list of endpoints for each API

Examples
